headline: Airbnb (ABNB): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Airbnb trades at $117.52 per share and has moved almost in lockstep with the market over the last six months. The stock has lost 10.9% while the S&P 500 is down 6.9%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
